   <text type="letter">
      <body><div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1896_AS_RBH_2_00005.jpeg"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr. Rich. Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#50" type="place">Wien</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#338" type="place">I. <hi rend="latintype">Wollzeile 15</hi></rs>,</addrLine><addrLine>4. Stock.</addrLine></address></div><div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><salute><pb facs="1896_AS_RBH_2_00004.jpeg"/>Lieber Richard.</salute></opener><p>Morgen geh ich ins <hi rend="latintype">Raimund</hi>theat (<rs type="work" ref="#43268">Ebne Erde u erſter Stock</rs>.)</p><p>Montag reiſe ich ſpäteſtens ab. <rs type="work" ref="#29899" subtype="implied"><hi rend="latintype">Première</hi></rs> ſchon am <date>31.</date> –</p><p>Schreib<unclear>en</unclear> Sie mir wo Sie morgen Abend ſind <hi rend="latintype">etc</hi>.</p><closer>Herzlich der Ihre<lb/><signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div></body>
